<html>
<head>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/style_login.css" type="text/css" />
  <script src="/static/jquery.js" type="text/javascript" ></script>
</head>

<body>
    <h1>设置登录密码</h1>
    <p>在这里，您可以设置控制台管理员的登陆密码：</p>
    <form action="${url}" method="post">
    <fieldset>
        <legend>设置新密码</legend>
        <ul>
          <li>
          <label>新登录密码</label><input type="password" name="new_password" value="${new_password}"/>
          </li>
          <li>
          <label></label><input type="submit" class="button" name="form.submitted" value="保存并重新登录"/>
          </li>
        </ul>
    </fieldset>
    </form>
</body>
</html>
